      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It is in absolutely stunning shape\u2014honestly, it feels just like it did the day it left the showroom! I have babied this car from day one, so you won't find a single blemish or a weird rattle anywhere. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for a new home. If you're looking for that 'brand new' feel without the 'brand new' price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and let's get you in for a test drive!",
