    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, complete with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is mechanically superlative; the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced, addressing the chassis' primary lateral stress concerns. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides crisp synchronization, feeding power to a variable M-differential lock with zero lash. The suspension retains its factory-spec kinematics, offering the precise, analog feedback purists demand. Finished in a deep, swirl-free luster with an immaculate Nappa leather interior, this vehicle represents a pinnacle of torsional rigidity and mechanical preservation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
